doctype html
html
    head
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')
    body
        #container(style='width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff;')
            #header(style='width: 390px; padding: 25px 0 15px; margin: 0 105px; border-bottom: 1px solid #334750; text-align: center;')
                img(src='https://stage-nora-science37.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/public-email-assets/science37-logo-white.png', alt='logo', style='height: 30.67px;	width: 100px;')
            if languageCode === 'ITA'
                #content(style='width: 390px; padding: 0 105px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F8F9F9;')
                    h4(style="color: #334750;	font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-weight: normal;	font-size: 26px;	line-height: 32px; margin: 40px 0 30px;") Benvenuto nella tua sperimentazione clinica
                    p(style="color: #334750;	font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;	line-height: 20px;") Pronto a iniziare? Scarica l’app della piattaforma Science 37 per completare la configurazione nel nostro sistema protetto e partecipare alla sperimentazione [#{trialName}].
                        br
                        br
                        span(style='font-weight: bold;') All’apertura dell’app, ti verrà chiesto di inserire questo codice:
                    div(style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0; color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;") #{code}
                    p(style="color: #334750;	font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;	line-height: 20px;") Non è mai stato così semplice partecipare a una sperimentazione clinica. Con la nostra app, puoi contattare il team di studio e monitorare in tempo reale tutti i dati che ti riguardano.
                    div(style='padding: 25px 0 15px; text-align: center;')
                        a(href='https://apps.apple.com/us/app/science-37-clinical-research/id1505694717', style='text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-right: 22px')
                            img(src='https://stage-nora-science37.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/public-email-assets/app-store-EN.png', alt='App Store', style='height: 46px; width: 142px;')
                        a(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.science37.mobile', style='text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;')
                            img(src='https://stage-nora-science37.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/public-email-assets/google-play-badge.png', alt='Google Play', style='height: 46px; width: 142px;')
                    p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;") Se non sei stato tu a fare la richiesta, ignora pure questa e-mail.
                    p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 28px;") Cordiali saluti,
                        br
                        span Il team Science 37
                #footer(style="padding: 34px 105px; background-color: #F8F9F9; color: #637381; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;	font-size: 12px;	line-height: 16px;	text-align: center;")
                    p Please do not respond to this email, as this inbox is not monitored. This email was automatically sent to you by our system.
                        br
                    span Science 37 - 12121 Bluff Creek Drive Suite 100 Los Angeles, CA 90094
                    div
                        br
                        a(href='https://www.science37.com/mobile-application-privacy-policy-italian/', style='color: #637381; text-decoration: none;') Privacy Policy

            else
                #content(style='width: 390px; padding: 0 105px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F8F9F9;')
                    h4(style="color: #334750;	font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-weight: normal;	font-size: 26px;	line-height: 32px; margin: 40px 0 30px;") Welcome to your clinical trial
                    p(style="color: #334750;	font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;	line-height: 20px;") Ready to get started? Download the Science 37 platform app to get set up in our secure system and participate in [#{trialName}] trial.
                        br
                        br
                        span(style='font-weight: bold;') Upon opening the app, you will be prompted to enter the following code:
                    div(style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0; color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;") #{code}
                    p(style="color: #334750;	font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;	line-height: 20px;") Being part of a clinical trial has never been easier. With our app, you can contact your study team and track all of your data in real time.
                    div(style='padding: 25px 0 15px; text-align: center;')
                        a(href='https://apps.apple.com/us/app/science-37-clinical-research/id1505694717', style='text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-right: 22px')
                            img(src='https://stage-nora-science37.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/public-email-assets/app-store-EN.png', alt='App Store', style='height: 46px; width: 142px;')
                        a(href='https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.science37.mobile', style='text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;')
                            img(src='https://stage-nora-science37.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/public-email-assets/google-play-badge.png', alt='Google Play', style='height: 46px; width: 142px;')
                    p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;") If you didn&apos;t make this request, you can ignore this email.
                    p(style="color: #334750; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; margin-top: 28px;") Sincerely,
                        br
                        span The Science 37 Team
                #footer(style="padding: 34px 105px; background-color: #F8F9F9; color: #637381; font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;	font-size: 12px;	line-height: 16px;	text-align: center;")
                    p Please do not respond to this email, as this inbox is not monitored. This email was automatically sent to you by our system.
                        br
                    span Science 37 - 12121 Bluff Creek Drive Suite 100 Los Angeles, CA 90094
                    div
                        br
                        a(href='https://www.science37.com/privacy-policy/', style='color: #637381; text-decoration: none;') Privacy Policy
